'''Lmɣrib''' iga yat sg tmizar ilan [[tafukt]] g wakal ns asggas kullut, ɣayan af Lmɣrib tswingm g ussufɣ n [[tazmrt]] sg tafukt. Lmɣrib gis uggar n 3000 n tsragt n tafukt g usggas, g [[Tanzruft|tnzruft]] n [[iẓẓlmḍ]] ar traḥa s 3600 n tsragt n tafukt. Lmɣrib iskr yan sg isntay imqqran n ussufɣ n tzmrt tafukant g [[Amaḍal|umaḍal]] s mayd igan 9,000,000,000,000 Dular. 

==Iwttasn ==
Awttas [[Yan|amzwaru]] n Lmɣrib g igr n tazmrt tafugant igat asyafu n 2000 migawaṭṭ g usggas n 2020. Bac Lmɣrib a ilkm iwttas ns g igr ad, iskr [[Tasnurayt tamɣribit n taẓḍaṛt tasulant]] (MASEN) g usggas n 2015. Lmɣrib tra a tlkm s usyafu n 38 % sg tazmrt taliktṛit isɣawsa.

